featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
``` *Nice Line..!*
,

 *I got life*
*To be of use to someone*.

 *But time is passing,*
*To earn pieces of paper*.

 *What will you do,*
*After earning so much money..???*

 *There is no 'pocket' in the shroud*,
*No cupboard in the grave..*'

 *And these are the angels of death*
*Don't even take 'bribe'*.

 *To the love of God*
*Who will destroy*?

 *All people are good*
*Who will commit the crime?*

 *"O God, these friends of mine*
*Keep safe...*

 *otherwise my safety*
*Who will pray??*

 *and keep mine*
*Enemies are also safe...*

 *Otherwise it's mine to come to you*
*Who will pray?"*

z *God said to me,*
*"Don't make so many friends*
*You will get cheated"*

 *I said* -
*"Oh God,*
*To those who read this message*
*If you get it*,

 *You too are deceived*
*Will become a friend*

 *name is short*
*But I keep a big heart*.

 *as much as money*
*I am not rich*.

 *but for my friends*
*to buy sorrow*
*I have status*.

 *I don't want to be the ace of spades*
*No queen's king*.

 *We are good jokers*
*whose luck will come*,

 *will turn the tables*||```
